表格Tab_Image的代码预览

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('Tab_Image')
and type = 'U')
drop table Tab_Image
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: Tab_Image */
/*==============================================================*/
create table Tab_Image (
TI_ID int identity,
TI_ProjectID int null,
TI_SubProjectID int null,
TI_NO int null,
TI_Image image null,
constraint PK_TAB_IMAGE primary key (TI_ID)
)
go

declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'合同图片表',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'Tab_Image'
go

declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'合同图片ID',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'Tab_Image', 'column', 'TI_ID'
go

declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'关联主项目',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'Tab_Image', 'column', 'TI_ProjectID'
go

declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'关联子项目',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'Tab_Image', 'column', 'TI_SubProjectID'
go
